{"tid":2043574,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[圍爐取暖] 國安法後，大家點樣應對？","createTime":"2020-05-30T13:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T07:12:03.000Z","uid":214189,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0903fc6c4991147c9f5e4db14d6150355110dcc0","tid":2043574,"uid":214189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"香港自上兩年開始經歷 中美貿易戰，反送中運動，武漢肺炎，負油價，到宜家國安法。身邊有朋友移民，做生意輸左好多錢，生活模式需要改變。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟只係想開個post 等大家可以交流下策略，互相安慰，渡過難關。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉 我先分享一下個人應對方案<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">資產配置</span></span><br />\nCurrent Asset<br />\n之前賺既今年都輸得7788<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不論本地/海外都首先平倉，負債歸零，Cash is King 留待其他用途<br />\n<br />\nNon-Cutrent Asset<br />\n減持少量香港物業，務求令全部債務歸零，公司保留充足現金流。<br />\n海外物業，全部保留，一係收租，一係必要時自住。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">風險管理</span></span><br />\n帶頭盔先 呢度講錯唔好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家最大問題係<br />\n1. 香港令人住得好無安全感，人生受到威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 中美關係惡化，唔知最後會衰成點，2019年都已經好難做，好多企業只係賺2%利潤，往後日子估計仲難捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n海外資產會盡保留，由其是唔係中國/美國/香港既資產，對沖返上面2個風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現金到手之後會轉錢到美國/澳洲/歐洲 都係想對沖風險，同埋就算去到外地都叫做有錢洗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己打算用transferwise，大銀碼有信心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">移民</span></span><br />\n好多國家都要坐幾年移民監，除非你去d細國。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時覺得只要有本BNO係手就已經覺得安心，希望英國第日會俾我哋住夠一年攞permanent resident，咁就舒服好多。雖然英國唔好住，但你有英國護照可以住歐盟其他國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 教育又好 有oxbridge imperial lse，又金融中心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去美國，美國同中國打緊，愈演愈烈，遲吓都未必安穩，加上福利唔好，臨老好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去台灣，宜家戰場係香港，完左之後下個就係台灣，加上經濟一直唔太好，下一代未必有能力移民返香港添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去澳洲，5年移民監，無哂青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">生意</span></span><br />\n現有業務，盡量精簡人手 cut cost，cut左咁多年都cut無可cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發展中業務，以投放金額小同靈活性高為前提下，會繼續進行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，90後出黎做野無幾年就要面對呢d野，真係好辛苦，我都想識返個女朋友簡簡單單過人世算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56eff33ca0a0abe6f6b3f499e03af546676485b7","tid":2043574,"uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"苟且偷生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0043593fe3c1eb6f03ae446b6bd88630bcea7d1b","tid":2043574,"uid":214189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56eff33ca0a0abe6f6b3f499e03af546676485b7","tid":2043574,"uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"苟且偷生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"無計，宜家搞到個個係度求生<br />\n返返去何鴻燊帶住10蚊去澳門既年代<br />\n根本無得嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b61132ba885047efccc19ea30dc654bb5ba189","tid":2043574,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":1